{"tid":209711,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"遇到有蝗蟲係你面前當街當行痾屎痾尿可以點做？","createTime":"2017-04-20T11:53:44.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-21T08:27:02.000Z","uid":49470,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"247cf7435f5d9544433f6bf13d8607221f3d43fe","tid":209711,"uid":49470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-20T11:53:44.000Z","msg":"岩岩準備入𨋢既時候見到有對講普通話母子唔出𨋢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n條仆街仔個背脊對住我而佢老母就踎左係佢隔離仲有佢老豆頂住左架𨋢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n個時唔知咩事一行埋去佢竟然係到<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">痾尿</span></span><br />\n最仆街既係我<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">淆底</span></span>走左去搭第二架𨋢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n究竟可以點做先可以兇撚到佢地還回香港人既霸氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"35750f24a1527c48ae607c0bacdfc976f5641012","tid":209711,"uid":97166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-20T11:58:30.000Z","msg":"走埋去隻腳90度向上抽，踢佢老尾春袋"},{"pid":"9e378c974fa3bd3378e389650a935b973e44664b","tid":209711,"uid":49470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-20T12:07:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>走埋去隻腳90度向上抽，踢佢老尾春袋</blockquote><br />\n屌咁d咪會整到成對鞋都係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"16a0caa4395a00bbc4da98c0f2609c159e6a77b6","tid":209711,"uid":49470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-20T12:08:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>走埋去隻腳90度向上抽，踢佢老尾春袋</blockquote><br />\n屌咁d<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">尿</span></span>咪會整到成對鞋都係<img src=\"/assets/fa